{"type": "article", "id": 12039, "title": "EVA 手工包", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-14T11:00:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060000108baN6UE2xPOSFQTJ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tLommer 是一家专门做手工包的公司，最近他们推出了三款 EVA 材料手工包，分别有 EvaOne，EvaTwo 和  Eva Clutch，其中  EvaOne 是一个有一根带子的中号单肩包，EvaTwo 可以让你在其中不同的颜色中选择喜欢的背带，而 Eva Clutch 则是一个中号的手拿包。所有的包袋都是由 EVA 材料制成，防水且轻便。<a href=\"http://www.lommer.gr/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359282gKLYwRvOyUnpiuW.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"543\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135929ABRTnlpwMte9v6uU.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"555\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.925\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135929830G5yhQ4MYbqS7r.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"449\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135930EAVp1dvqiRkK3OFX.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135930FTm67QqVgMojC40e.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"446\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}